name: amazonaws-com-appstream-connector
description:
Amazon AppStream 2.0 This is the Amazon AppStream 2.0 API Reference. This reference provides
descriptions and syntax for each of the actions and data types in AppStream 2.0.
AppStream 2.0 is a fully managed application streaming service. You centrally
manage your desktop applications on AppStream 2.0 and securely deliver them to
any computer. AppStream 2.0 manages the AWS resources required to host and run
your applications, scales automatically, and provides access to your users on
demand.

To learn more about AppStream 2.0, see the following resources:

 *   Amazon AppStream 2.0 product page [http://aws.amazon.com/appstream2] 
   
   
 *   Amazon AppStream 2.0 documentation
   [http://aws.amazon.com/documentation/appstream2]
